      </div>
      <div class="bring-item">
        <span class="bring-icon">💉</span>
        <span class="bring-text"><strong>Vaccination records</strong> — any prior immunization booklet or records from childhood</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bring-item">
        <span class="bring-icon">📋</span>
        <span class="bring-text"><strong>Medical history</strong> — list of any chronic conditions, surgeries, or medications</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bring-item">
        <span class="bring-icon">💊</span>
        <span class="bring-text"><strong>Current medications</strong> — bring bottles or a list with dosages</span>
      </div>
